title: BRIEF-Pieris Pharmaceuticals Prices Public Offering Of 5.50 Mln Common Shares At $8/Share
text: February 14, 2018 / 5:31 AM / in 39 minutes BRIEF-Pieris Pharmaceuticals Prices Public Offering Of 5.50 Mln Common Shares At $8/Share Reuters Staff Feb 14 (Reuters) - Pieris Pharmaceuticals Inc: * PIERIS PHARMACEUTICALS ANNOUNCES PRICING OF ITS PUBLIC OFFERING * SAYS PUBLIC OFFERING OF 5.50 MILLION COMMON SHARES PRICED AT $8.00PER SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ( Bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com )
